Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Symbolism=Solar Symbolism
  - 816
By: Al-Ghazâlî
---
Remember it is the heart and not the body which strives to draw near
to God. By ‘heart’ I do not mean the flesh perceived by the senses,
but that secret thing which is sometimes expressed by spirit, and
sometimes by soul.
